WHat remains, is only to deduce ſome profitable Inferences, Doctrinal and Practical, immediately from the Text in its Coherence and Scope, and ſuch only as are clearly included in the Bowels of it. To direct wherein, I ſhall make 2 Tim. 3.16. my Card and Compaſs. All Scripture is Divinely inſpir'd, and profitable, for Doctrine,


for Evidence,

